OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry, perhaps a little
OL,7,Fbrightness across Orkney. Then the
OL,8,Frest of the night will be mainly dry
OL,9,Falthough some low cloud around.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FDry with variable amounts
OL,12,Fof cloud, some sunshine likely to
OL,13,Fbreak through at times. Light winds.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,16,FStaying largely dry and settled
OL,17,Falthough a fair amount of cloud around
OL,18,Fat times. Some brighter spells too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
